The evidence with the title 'The Global Nutrition Transition: the Pandemic Of Obesity ' says Clearly diets and activity patterns had changed drastically in the US and by the 1980's we understood that the dietary quality of US diets were worsening, physical activity was drastically reduced, and  ...  ... The thinking is that since we shifted dietary patterns greatly in a matter of 10 to 20 years, we can shift back just as readily. 
